    <description>When a Ticket Assignee is created, this flow aggregates the names of all assignees to the same Ticket into a comma separated list and sets as the Assignee(s) field on the Ticket.

Sends bell notifications to the Requestor and Assignee. Sends a notification email to the Assignee.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <description>Formats the assignee name with a comma as appropriate to create a comma separated list</description>
        <name>f_AssigneeName</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
       {!varAssigneeNames} = Null, {!Loop_Assignees.pro_Assigned_To__r.FirstName} + &apos; &apos; + {!Loop_Assignees.pro_Assigned_To__r.LastName}    , &apos;, &apos; + {!Loop_Assignees.pro_Assigned_To__r.FirstName} + &apos; &apos; + {!Loop_Assignees.pro_Assigned_To__r.LastName} )</expression>
    </formulas>
    <interviewLabel>Prodigy - Ticket Assignee - Set Assignee(s) &amp; Send Notifications On Ticket On Create {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
    <label>Prodigy - Ticket Assignee - Set Assignee(s) &amp; Send Notifications On Ticket On Create</label>
